get the rat source
	svn checkout http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/radartools/trunk
		or 
	wget http://download.berlios.de/radartools/rat_v0.20_source.tar.gz
		tar zxf rat_v0.20_source.tar.gz
		cd rat_v0.20

start the idl
	idl
	IDL> .r rat_install
	IDL> rat_install
	IDL> exit

have a nice fun
	./rat
